              <p>Geographic Optimization (GO) or Local SEO which is sometimes how it is known helps your business appear in local searches by showing search engines and AI tools that you are a trusted local business.</p>
              <p>Local SEO makes your business appear when people search for:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-3 space-y-2">
                <li>"best [your service] near me"</li>
                <li>"[your service] in [your town or city]"</li>
                <li>"[your service] open now"</li>
              </ul>
              <p>With good Local SEO, your business shows up in map results, the local pack (those businesses Google shows at the top with a map), and local directories.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

